she may never come off it.

758
00:32:42,461 --> 00:32:45,173
Possibly. Possibly, but she
suffered a massive stroke

759
00:32:45,197 --> 00:32:47,675
from which she
probably will not recover.

760
00:32:47,699 --> 00:32:51,612
Mr. Walton, I cannot
give you percentages.

761
00:32:51,636 --> 00:32:54,454
Extremely unlikely.

762
00:32:56,274 --> 00:32:57,836
We understand
your sister's wishes

763
00:32:57,860 --> 00:33:00,972
