alive by artificial means.

764
00:33:00,996 --> 00:33:02,956
Judy. Would you
like to talk to her?

765
00:33:08,037 --> 00:33:09,948
Yes, if we don't
intubate her, she will die,

766
00:33:09,972 --> 00:33:12,316
but the chances of a mean...

767
00:33:12,340 --> 00:33:15,776
The chances of a
meaningful recovery are ex...

768
00:33:17,796 --> 00:33:19,862
I understand.

769
00:33:22,700 --> 00:33:24,167
Yes. Goodbye.

770
00:33:30,409 --> 00:33:32,520
Hey, you. Malatucci.
Come here. Malucci.

771
00:33:32,544 --> 00:33:36,224
Whatever. Look, wave you
seen the OIG officer down here?

772
00:33:36,248 --> 00:33:37,392
Who?

773
00:33:37,416 --> 00:33:38,560
Deputy inspector general.

774
00:33:38,584 --> 00:33:40,361
Regulates our
Medicare compliance.

775
00:33:40,385 --> 00:33:42,029
I heard she was snooping around.

776
00:33:42,053 --> 00:33:43,631
Short, battle-ax, humorless?

777
00:33:43,655 --> 00:33:45,032
That's her. Curtain Two.

778
00:33:45,056 --> 00:33:46,167
Thank you.

779
00:33:46,191 --> 00:33:48,869
Dr. Benton told you
you needed surgery?

780
00:33:48,893 --> 00:33:50,004
He brought me upstairs.

781
00:33:50,028 --> 00:33:51,505
Why didn't he operate?

782
00:33:51,529 --> 00:33:53,574
